An incredible 3 days that has left my heart and mind so full! 10 days before the event I decided to travel from India to attend this event, because I knew this whole experience in itself was our reward. And WHAT A REWARD it was✨

The most thoughtfully curated event, with connections so intimate and insights so rich, and hospitality so generous - helmed by @imranamed and @priyarao and the entire team of @bof and @businessofbeauty , this was THE MOST enriching event and experience I’ve been too. If you get the chance you should watch the full videos on their website but I’m attaching some really great pearls of wisdom from a few of the sessions (last slides). 

Met my favourite founder @danessa_myricks who has inspired me so much to lead a brand with true authenticity and kindness. When you meet her you know why just about everyone loves her so much. She truly has the kindest eyes🤍 

Last but the most favourite part of this experience was meeting my fellow inaugural cohort of finalists. Each founder’s story has inspired me so so much. Every single one has hustled their way up to building their brands and identity in such a unique way and it’s left me in awe. I made friends for life, and I can’t wait to welcome them to India someday soon :)

Thank you again Imran and Priya, you created magic and I’m excited to be back soon next year!💫

Special shout out to @jaelaaliyah, @niamh_ec, @alicegividen @danielakmorosini, @liz_flora and the rest of the BoF and BoB team for their impeccable efforts in making this event so seamless for us!🤍

Your skin’s wishlist just went travel-sized 😍✈️

Been wanting to try d’you but couldn’t commit? We get it. That’s why the minis are finally here!

Perfect for testing, tossing in your travel pouch, or just falling in love before going full size 💅💖

Pick from singles, duos, or trios - whatever suits your skincare vibe 🧴✨

Exclusively now on Nykaa! 🛍️

I am NOT a lip girlie. I’m not someone who hoards lip balms, chapsticks, lipsticks or that girl who can’t wait to get the latest lip stain. I’m someone who wants to feel NOTHING on my lips, and I don’t care to reapply much on my lips either. 

And I’m working on more than a few lip formulas at the moment🙈. So naturally I’m focused on creating textures that ~feel like nothing~ yet do everything as expected. Lip nectar was exactly that. It’s a lightweight formula that will absolutely not sit on your lips. It was designed to get the job done and disappear. It will soften the driest lips and then vanish. It’ll heal severely cracked lips within minutes (no jokes) and then softy make its presence thin. This was intentional. 

The aim of a lip balm is to heal dry lips. But with thicker balms that sit on your skin, our mind gets accustomed to want to keep having that feeling. Ever heard of the reverse phenomenon where the more you apply the drier your lips feel without it? It’s not that your lips are actually getting drier without the lip balm, it’s just that your baseline has changed, and your mind is now used to feeling a coat of something sitting on your lips - so bare lips without anything even in their normal natural state start to feel dry. This is just cognitive bias, not an actual hydration problem. 

With lip nectar we wanted to create a formula that heals without being loud. The in-between texture of lip nectar does exactly that - it’s quiet & effortless in its presence, it dutifully does its job of healing, it doesn’t leave behind a streak of wax, and you’ll just naturally find your lips softened without needing to reapply it too often.

Those that prefer thicker lip balms - fair play this may not be your new love :) 
As for me, I’m slowly converting to a lip girlie since we are developing so many new lip formulas👀
Do you like minimalist / effortless formulas? Or are you a long-wear, bold lip girlie? What would you like to see from us in lip textures next?

latestPosts.caption:
With 4 of our products nominated for the prestigious @vogueindia Vogue Beauty Awards, we were definitely excited to see which one gets the official seal of approval. Beyond thrilled that 2 of our products scored 3 awards!!🥳 good grease did a double whammy with securing not only the Jury’s Choice but also the Reader’s Choice award in the cleansing balm / makeup remover category. She is officially THAT girl🙌🏻 Anyone who’s tried GG has raved about this product, and I can confidently say this is one of the BEST cleansing balm products in the market👏🏻

inbalance toner is one of my favs from our portfolio, and she’s a silent flame like our cult IMD moisturiser. You don’t know what’s the big deal about this one until you add it in your routine, and then realise you can’t do skincare without this in the routine anymore😄

Super proud of my team who work so hard to bring each of our precious products to life in their most unique ways🫶🏻

A heartfelt thank you to team @vogueindia @condenastindia and @rochelle.pinto for organising and bringing back this prestigious IP, and recognising so many budding beauty brands🤍 and to @tirabeauty for supporting this initiative💕
